[2026-07-22 19:36:56] ADMIN: 113980311909370790584 | ACTION: Create Bulletin Event | RESOURCE: N/A | DETAILS: BulletinEvent(id=null, title=Adobe University Hackathon 2026, description=The Adobe University Hackathon 2026 is a national-level innovation competition hosted by Adobe on Unstop, open to engineering students across all years and branches. It's designed to simulate real-world engineering challenges and puts your skills in AI, full-stack development, DSA, problem-solving, and product design to the test — with a shot at direct visibility before Adobe's engineering leadership.

Team Rules

Teams of 2–3 members
All members must be from the same college/university
Cross-year and cross-specialization teams are allowed; cross-college teams are not
Each participant may be part of only one team
Register using your official university email (Gmail accepted if unavailable) and a valid WhatsApp number

Competition Format — 4 Rounds

Online Assessment (90 min, single attempt): 15 MCQs on algorithms/DSA/programming logic, 1 coding question, and 1 brand-visibility case study
Development Round: Shortlisted teams get the official problem statement and build a complete solution, submitting a GitHub repo with supporting docs
Prototype Showcase: Top teams build and demo a functional prototype (only the team leader submits)
Grand Finale: Top teams present to Adobe's leadership at Adobe's Noida HQ — travel and accommodation fully covered

Rewards

Winning team: MacBook Pro each
Runner-up team: MacBook Neo each
Top 50 participants: PPIs + Adobe internship opportunity (₹1,10,000/month stipend; PPI eligibility limited to the 2028 graduating batch)
National finalists: Adobe merchandise + sponsored HQ visit
Top 50 teams: official Adobe participation certificates, coverImage=https://pub-6d28afd560b0498d9fea3f401d07e798.r2.dev/bulletin-events/113980311909370790584/071ff123-04a4-4bce-97cd-c2e31e338357.png, externalLink=https://unstop.com/hackathons/crp-adobe-university-hackathon-2026-adobe-1715333, eventStartDate=2026-08-09T08:30:00Z, eventEndDate=2026-09-27T18:29:00Z, registrationEndDate=2026-08-08T18:29:00Z, conductedBy=Adobe (hosted via Unstop), global=true, collegeIds=[], active=true, deleted=false, createdAt=null, updatedAt=null, deletedAt=null) | STATUS: SUCCESS
